TITLE: Adding libgraph Dependency in Elixir Mix Project
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet shows how to add libgraph as a dependency in a Mix project's deps function. It specifies the version constraint for the library.
SOURCE: https://github.com/bitwalker/libgraph/blob/main/README.md#2025-04-19_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: elixir
CODE:
```
def deps do
  [{:libgraph, "~> 0.16.0"}]
end
```

TITLE: Defining N3 Prefixes and Edge Data for Hamsterster Friendships Network
DESCRIPTION: This snippet defines the N3 (Notation3) prefixes and edge data representations for the Hamsterster friendships network. It specifies the URI prefix for members, declares the type of entities as foaf:Person, and defines bidirectional friendship relationships using foaf:knows predicates.
SOURCE: https://github.com/bitwalker/libgraph/blob/main/test/fixtures/petster/metadata.txt#2025-04-19_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: n3
CODE:
```
n3-prefix-m: konect_petster_friendships_hamster: <http://konect.uni-koblenz.de/networks/petster-friendships-hamster/Member/> .
n3-type-m: foaf:Person
n3-edgedata-1: $m foaf:knows $n .
n3-edgedata-2: $n foaf:knows $m .
```
